Class AbstractPokemon

  • java.lang.Object
    • tcg.AbstractCard
      • tcg.AbstractPokemon
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICard, IPokemon, Visitable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractElectricPokemon, AbstractFightingPokemon, AbstractFirePokemon, AbstractGrassPokemon, AbstractPsychicPokemon, AbstractWaterPokemon

    public abstract class AbstractPokemon
extends AbstractCard
implements IPokemon
    The base class for all the Pokemon. Contains getter and some setter methods for the Pokemon's properties. Also contains the attack method according to the type of attack.
